OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSome patchy rain across the
OL,6,FSouthern Uplands at first this
OL,7,Fmorning. Otherwise a dry day with some
OL,8,Fbright or sunny spells breaking
OL,9,Fthrough by this afternoon. Feeling
OL,10,Fwarm in any afternoon sunshine.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry. The
OL,13,Frest of the night will be mainly dry
OL,14,Falthough rather cloudy, perhaps a
OL,15,Flittle light rain developing across
OL,16,Fthe Southern Uplands at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
