OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FDry in the morning with
OL,6,Fsome bright spells. Then rain will
OL,7,Fspread southeast during the afternoon,
OL,8,Falthough the far southeast dry until
OL,9,Flater.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FDry
OL,12,Fon Thursday. Unsettled with showers or
OL,13,Flonger spells of rain on Friday and
OL,14,FSaturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
